fields.label: Instructions
fields.message:
Select the Practice Areas and Industries to be listed on the following pages:

- Practice Areas & Industries
- Events (News category)
- Publications (News category)

sub_fields.label: Email
sub_fields.name: email
sub_fields.instructions: Enter the email address where resumes should be sent.

fields.label: Banner Image
fields.name: banner_image
fields.instructions: This image shows at the top of the inside of the Post, instead of showing the Featured image.

fields.label: Display Date
fields.name: display_date
fields.instructions: If a display date is entered, it will show in place of the date this post was published.

fields.label: Exclude this post from the Home Page
fields.name: exclude_this_post_from_the_home_page

fields.label: Mailing Address and Phone
fields.name: mailing_address
fields.instructions: Enter the mailing address and phone number.

fields.label: Driving Directions Link
fields.name: driving_directions_link
fields.instructions: Add a Google Maps link to this address.

fields.label: Industry Name
fields.name: industry_name
fields.instructions: Enter the name that should appear when this is listed as an Industry.

fields.label: Practice Area Name
fields.name: practice_area_name
fields.instructions: Enter the name that should appear when this is listed as a Practice Area.

fields.label: Search Filter Name
fields.name: search_filter_name
fields.instructions:
Enter name in this format: Last Name, First Name Middle Initial
Example: Ambrose, Dillon J.

fields.label: Title
fields.name: title
fields.instructions: Enter a title for this attorney. Example: Shareholder

fields.label: Support Staff
fields.name: support_staff
fields.instructions: Check this box if this person is not an attorney.

fields.label: Portrait Image
fields.name: portrait_image
fields.instructions: Add an image for this attorney. Image should be 244px width, 305px height.

fields.label: Thumbnail Image
fields.name: thumbnail_image
fields.instructions: Image size should be 40px width, 50px height.

sub_fields.label: Section Heading
sub_fields.name: section_heading
sub_fields.instructions: Enter text for the section heading. Example: Appellate Experience

sub_fields.label: Leadership Item Text
sub_fields.name: leadership_item_text
sub_fields.instructions: Enter the Leadership item text. Example:  Member, Waukesha County Bar Association

sub_fields.label: Recognition Text
sub_fields.name: recognition_text
sub_fields.instructions: Enter text for this item. Example: Wisconsin Super Lawyers Magazine - Business Litigation (2017)

sub_fields.label: Education Text
sub_fields.name: education_text
sub_fields.instructions: Enter text for this education item. Example: J.D., cum laude, Marquette University Law School
